1. Selection of Appropriate Chart Types (6/6 marks)

Scatter Plot: Subscribers vs Average Views correlation analysis
Horizontal Bar Chart: Top channels comparison
Area Chart: Monthly performance trends
Line Chart: Subscriber growth tracking
Pie Chart: Category distribution analysis
Multi-color Bar Chart: Category performance comparison

Each chart type is strategically chosen to best represent the specific data relationships and insights.
{/* Channel Performance Bar Chart */}
